<p>Added a dedicated .htaccess analysis engine.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Detects PHP handlers assigned to static extensions such as .jpg, .png, .gif and .txt.</li>
  <li>Detects auto_prepend_file and auto_append_file directives.</li>
  <li>Detects PHP/JS code markers inside .htaccess, including &lt;?php, &lt;script, eval( and base64_decode(.</li>
  <li>Detects suspicious RewriteRule and RewriteCond directives, including rewrites to wp-login.php, cache.php, shell/tmp files and parameterized index.php targets.</li>
  <li>Detects WordPress markers inside Bitrix projects: wp-config.php, wp-login.php, wp-admin, wp-content, wp-includes.</li>
  <li>Detects access bypass directives in sensitive directories: /upload, /bitrix/modules, /bitrix/php_interface.</li>
  <li>Added dedicated htaccess_* signatures and smoke tests for the .htaccess analyzer.</li>
</ul>